com.pushwoosh.fragment

Class PushFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • com.pushwoosh.fragment.PushFragment
  • Deprecated. 
    As of release 5.0.0, replaced by Pushwoosh

    @Deprecated
public class PushFragment
extends Fragment

    PushFragment encapsulates the Pushwoosh logic.

    In order to set up Pushwoosh via PushFragment you should follow these steps:

  • PushFragment's parent Activity should implements PushEvenListener
  • In the onCreate method of PushFragment's parent activity you should invoke init(FragmentActivity)
  • Don't forget to invoke PushFragment#checkMessage(android.content.Intent intent) on android.app.Activity#onNewIntent(android.content.Intent intent) method of PushFragment's parent activity
